{"EN":[{"def":"Half an em, that is, half of the unit of space in measuring printed matter.","pos":""}],"EN BLOC":[{"def":"In a lump; as a whole; all together.","pos":""}],"EN PASSANT":[{"def":"In passing; in the course of any procedure; -- said specif.","pos":""},{"def":"of the taking of an adverse pawn which makes a first move of two squares by a pawn already so advanced as to threaten the first of these squares.","pos":""}],"EN RAPPORT":[{"def":"In accord, harmony, or sympathy; having a mutual, esp.","pos":""}],"EN ROUTE":[{"def":"On the way or road.","pos":""}],"EN-":[{"def":"A prefix signifying in or into, used in many English words, chiefly those borrowed from the French.","pos":""},{"def":"An adjectival suffix, meaning made of; as in golden, leaden, wooden.","pos":""}]}